'''德州參議院第五議案'''（{{lang-en|Texas Senate Bill 5}}）建立於2013年6月11日，是[[德克薩斯州|德克薩斯州]]第八十三屆立法會議正在討論的一項議案。

== 議案內容 ==
德州參議院第五議案將提出一系列措施，將就德克薩斯州現行的墮胎法案的條款進行增加和更新。其中最重要的條款包括：將禁止墮胎的時限從妊娠24周縮短為妊娠20周；将全州的47间堕胎所减为5间，并全都位于德州东部，且要求從事墮胎手術的醫生僅能在他所屬的醫院內實施墮胎手術；所有從事墮胎手術的診所的手術室必須達到符合所有手術的醫療標準。<ref>{{cite news|title=Wendy Davis took on Texas bullies on abortion and won|author=Abcarian, R.|url=http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-wendy-davis-took-on-texas-bullies-on-abortion-and-won-20130626,0,5588133.story|newspaper=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]|date=2013-06-26|accessdate=2013-06-26|archive-date=2013-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004235816/http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-wendy-davis-took-on-texas-bullies-on-abortion-and-won-20130626,0,5588133.story|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Texas abortion bill falls after challenge |url=http://www.theeagle.com/news/texas/article_7696dc9f-39c4-5b9d-a5d4-d7349f021e5f.html |newspaper=鷹報 |date=2013-06-26 |agency=[[美聯社|美聯社]] |accessdate=2013-06-26 |archive-date=2013-06-28 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130628042854/http://www.theeagle.com/news/texas/article_7696dc9f-39c4-5b9d-a5d4-d7349f021e5f.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Dewhurst declares abortion bill dead, blames 'unruly mob' |first1=Chuck |last1=Lindell |first2=Mike |last2=Ward |url=http://www.statesman.com/news/news/davis-starts-filibuster-to-stop-abortion-bill/nYTqs/ |newspaper=Austin American-Statesman |date=2013-06-26 |accessdate=2013-06-27 |archive-date=2016-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160810071558/http://www.statesman.com/news/news/davis-starts-filibuster-to-stop-abortion-bill/nYTqs/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.capitol.state.tx.us/tlodocs/831/billtext/html/SB00005I.htm|title=83(1) SB 5 - Introduced Version - Bill Text|publisher=Texas Legislature Online|accessdate=2013-06-02|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304114844/http://www.capitol.state.tx.us/tlodocs/831/billtext/html/SB00005I.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 此外，該議案還要求婦女在服用墮胎藥（例如：[[美服培酮|美服培酮]]）時必須接受監督。<ref name="FWStar07102013" />

== 表决歷史 ==
=== 第一次特別會議 ===
2013年5月25日，參議員[[溫迪·戴維思|溫迪·戴維思]]女士為阻擾該議案而採取了[[冗長辯論|冗長辯論]]的措施。直到當日午夜，由於特別會議時間已經結束，因此該議案的投票階段已流產。<ref>{{cite news|title=Marathon filibuster: Overnight drama stalls Texas abortion vote |author=Tomlinson, C.; Vertuno, J. |url=http://www.khou.com/news/texas-news/Texas-senator-filibusters-against-abortion-bill--212983501.html |newspaper=KHOU |date=2013-06-26 |accessdate=2013-06-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130628073423/http://www.khou.com/news/texas-news/Texas-senator-filibusters-against-abortion-bill--212983501.html |archivedate=2013-06-28 }}</ref> 經過十小時的[[冗長辯論|冗長辯論]]之後，副州長{{Link-en|大衛·杜赫斯特|David Dewhurst}}裁定戴維思在談論超聲波檢查法案時偏離主題，要求全體議員就冗長辯論是否能繼續進行而投票。<ref>{{cite news|title=Lawmaker's filibuster to kill Texas abortion bill ends early|author=Sutton, J.; Smith, M.|url=http://www.cnn.com/2013/06/25/politics/texas-abortion-bill/|newspaper=[[CNN|CNN]]|date=2013-06-25|accessdate=2013-06-26|archive-date=2021-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210727230600/https://www.cnn.com/2013/06/25/politics/texas-abortion-bill/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 儘管共和黨方面努力想通過該議案，但是在參議員{{Link-en|萊蒂西亞·范·德·普特|Leticia R. Van de Putte}}女士和其他參議員的質詢下，投票過程再度中斷。直到午夜時刻的到來，在本屆特別會議結束前，該議案並沒有獲得通過。<ref name=yeaornay>{{cite news|last=King|first=Michael|title=Yea or Nay?|url=http://www.austinchronicle.com/blogs/news/2013-06-26/yea-or-nay/|newspaper=The Austin Chronicle|date=2013-06-26|accessdate=2013-06-26|archive-date=2013-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019064638/http://www.austinchronicle.com/blogs/news/2013-06-26/yea-or-nay/|dead-url=no}}</ref>  截止日期后，共和黨宣佈在截止日期前已經投票并以“19比11”的結果通過了該議案；但是民主黨人卻宣稱該投票發生在截止日期后，因此是無效的。<ref name=yeaornay/> 副州長杜赫斯特後來承認該議案並未在規定時間內投票而導致流產。<ref>{{cite news|title=Liveblog: Senators Trying to Determine if Abortion Bill Passed|url=http://www.texastribune.org/2013/06/26/dems-approach-abortion-victory-special-session-wan/|newspaper=The Texas Tribune|date=2013-06-26|accessdate=2013-06-26|archive-date=2022-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220110083844/https://www.texastribune.org/2013/06/26/dems-approach-abortion-victory-special-session-wan/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Guardian62613>{{cite news|title=Wendy Davis filibuster and public protest defeat Texas abortion bill: Texas senator stages 11-hour filibuster to block bill • Vote derailed, lieutenant governor blames 'mob'|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2013/jun/26/texas-abortion-vote-defeated-deadline-wendy-davis|accessdate=2013-06-26|newspaper=[[衛報|衛報]]|date=2013-06-26|author=Helen Davidson|archive-date=2013-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130723145638/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2013/jun/26/texas-abortion-vote-defeated-deadline-wendy-davis|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==== 時間戳問題 ====
在德州參議院第五議案被以為通過之後，有關該法案的通過歷史被記錄在官方網頁上，顯示該法案在2013年6月26日獲得通過。<ref>{{cite news|title=Texas Legislature Changes Timestamps on SB5 Votes|author=Gill, K.|url=http://themoderatevoice.com/183478/texas-legislature-changes-timestamps-on-sb5-votes/|newspaper=The Moderate Voice|date=2013-06-26|accessdate=2013-06-26|archive-date=2015-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151006034413/http://themoderatevoice.com/183478/texas-legislature-changes-timestamps-on-sb5-votes/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 但是隨後，這個頁面被撤下。而在新更新的頁面上，法案的通過時間被修改為6月25日。<ref name="IBTimes">{{cite news|title=Changing Timestamp Mystery Continues After Texas Abortion Bill Defeat, Wendy Davis Filibuster|author=Poladian, C.|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/changing-timestamp-mystery-continues-after-texas-abortion-bill-defeat-wendy-davis-filibuster-1324549#|newspaper=International Business Times|date=2013-06-26|accessdate=2013-06-26|archive-date=2021-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423113146/https://www.ibtimes.com/changing-timestamp-mystery-continues-after-texas-abortion-bill-defeat-wendy-davis-filibuster-1324549|dead-url=no}}</ref> 根據德克薩斯州刑法第37.10節的規定，對政府記錄文件作出虛假改變是違法行為。<ref name=IBTimes /><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.statutes.legis.state.tx.us/Docs/PE/htm/PE.37.htm |title=PENAL CODE CHAPTER 37. PERJURY AND OTHER FALSIFICATION<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2013-07-13 |archive-date=2018-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180309224733/http://www.statutes.legis.state.tx.us/Docs/PE/htm/PE.37.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref> 根據德克薩斯州立法參考圖書館所述，德克薩斯立法在線（{{lang|en|Texas Legislature Online}}）系統“並不是一個官方的記錄機構，（德克薩斯州立法參考圖書館成員）進入德克薩斯立法在線工作僅僅是基於公共服務，而這一切和德州眾議院及參議院無關。”<ref>{{cite news|title=Confusion, not conspiracy, to blame for abortion vote controversy|author=Wiggins, M.|url=http://www.kvue.com/news/Sources-Confusion-not-conspiracy-to-blame-for-abortion-vote-controversy-213584471.html|publisher=KVUE|date=2013-06-29|accessdate=2013-06-29|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130629100002/http://www.kvue.com/news/Sources-Confusion-not-conspiracy-to-blame-for-abortion-vote-controversy-213584471.html|archivedate=2013-06-29}}</ref> 公共誠信局在接到投訴后著手調查該事件。<ref>{{cite news|title=Public Integrity Unit reviewing date change on SB5 vote|url=http://www.kxan.com/dpp/news/texas_lege/piu-reviewing-time-change-on-sb5-vote|publisher=KXAN|date=2013-06-29|accessdate=2013-06-29|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130630125111/http://www.kxan.com/dpp/news/texas_lege/piu-reviewing-time-change-on-sb5-vote|archivedate=2013-06-30}}</ref>

=== 第二次特別會議 ===
6月26日，德州州長[[裡克·佩裡|裡克·佩裡]]將這項議案添加成為一個三項議案并提請召開第二次特別會議進行討論。<ref>{{cite news|title=Texas Gov. Rick Perry calls 2nd special session to pass abortion bill|author=|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-250_162-57591221/texas-gov-rick-perry-calls-2nd-special-session-to-pass-abortion-bill/|newspaper=哥倫比亞廣播公司新聞台|date=2013-06-26|accessdate=2013-06-26|archive-date=2013-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029155115/http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-250_162-57591221/texas-gov-rick-perry-calls-2nd-special-session-to-pass-abortion-bill/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Texas Gov. Perry calls second special session on abortion|author=美聯社|url=http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2013/06/26/texas-gov-perry-calls-second-special-session-on-abortion/|newspaper=福斯新聞台|date=2013-06-26|accessdate=2013-06-26|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924142815/http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2013/06/26/texas-gov-perry-calls-second-special-session-on-abortion/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 佩裡認為這樣做是因為“日益崩壞的禮儀和體統，德州的人民選舉我們來阻止這樣的事情擴大化。”<ref>{{cite news|title=New life for Texas abortion bill blocked by Wendy Davis|author=|url=http://m.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-23074659|newspaper=英國廣播公司新聞台|date=2013-06-26|accessdate=2013-06-26}}</ref>

隨著第二次特別會議的召開，支持者和反對者都召集了大量民眾聚集在德州立法大廈周圍。他們站在他們所支持的一邊，身穿藍色或橙色的T恤。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.texastribune.org/2013/06/24/abortion-protests-redistricting-special-session-ne/ |title=Abortion, Protests, Transportation as Session Nears End {{!}} The Texas Tribune<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2013-07-13 |archive-date=2021-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211226114622/https://www.texastribune.org/2013/06/24/abortion-protests-redistricting-special-session-ne/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2013年7月10日，德州眾議院以“96比49”的投票結果通過了該議案。<ref name="FWStar07102013">Tinsley, Anna. [http://www.star-telegram.com/2013/07/10/4993347/texas-house-gives-its-final-approval.html Texas House gives its final approval to new abortion restrictions] {{Wayback|url=http://www.star-telegram.com/2013/07/10/4993347/texas-house-gives-its-final-approval.html |date=20141129035239 }}, 沃斯堡新電報, July 10, 2013</ref>德州參議院以“19比11”的投票結果通過了該議案。德州州長裡克·佩裡7月18日其後簽署成為法律。

== 公眾評論 ==
對此議案持支持和反對意見的機構和個人在[[Twitter|Twitter]]及德州論壇上分享各自的觀點并獲取最新的訊息，幾個與本議案相關的主題標籤（{{lang|en|hashtags}}）也變得熱門起來。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ibtimes.com/standwithwendy-social-media-erupts-sen-wendy-davis-filibusters-abortion-bill-1323743 |title=#StandWithWendy: Social Media Erupts As Sen. Wendy Davis Filibusters Abortion Bill<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2013-07-15 |archive-date=2019-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190530221229/https://www.ibtimes.com/standwithwendy-social-media-erupts-sen-wendy-davis-filibusters-abortion-bill-1323743 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blogs.marketwatch.com/capitolreport/2013/06/26/wendy-davis-and-the-peoples-filibuster-cries-victory-for-social-media-too/ |title=Wendy Davis and the people's filibuster cries victory for social media too - Capitol Report - MarketWatch<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2013-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130701235901/http://blogs.marketwatch.com/capitolreport/2013/06/26/wendy-davis-and-the-peoples-filibuster-cries-victory-for-social-media-too/ |archive-date=2013-07-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cnn.com/2013/06/26/tech/social-media/texas-filibuster-twitter |title=Texas filibuster on abortion bill rivets online - CNN.com<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2013-07-15 |archive-date=2021-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210509151528/https://www.cnn.com/2013/06/26/tech/social-media/texas-filibuster-twitter |dead-url=no }}</ref> 由於對這場會議的直播和討論，使得整場辯論不僅在全美引起討論，甚至還引發了國際上的關注。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.npr.org/blogs/itsallpolitics/2013/07/05/197987945/a-lively-political-press-in-a-state-where-everything-s-bigger |title=A Lively Political Press In A State Where Everything's Bigger : It's All Politics : NPR<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2013-07-15 |archive-date=2015-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150425081146/http://www.npr.org/blogs/itsallpolitics/2013/07/05/197987945/a-lively-political-press-in-a-state-where-everything-s-bigger |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 爭議 ===
反對者認為，如果迫使墮胎診所將其手術室標準提高到與醫院一個水平，勢必將導致大量診所的關閉，這將使得本州的女性無法尋求到診所的幫助。<ref name="NYTimes06252013">{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/06/25/us/texas-house-restricts-abortions-in-a-move-that-could-force-clinics-to-shut.html?_r=0 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2013-07-15 |archive-date=2021-07-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210720211435/https://www.nytimes.com/2013/06/25/us/texas-house-restricts-abortions-in-a-move-that-could-force-clinics-to-shut.html?_r=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 但是支持者卻認為，該議案旨在保護孕婦和未出生嬰兒的健康和安全。<ref name="NYTimes06252013" />

